  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Category:</strong> Clan <br /><strong>Prerequisites:</strong> Fon Clan or Shihōin Clan, Level 8+ <br />(You must have the <em><strong>Way of Onmitsu: Shunpo</strong></em> jutsu on your jutsu list) <br />Your Shunpo knowledge and experience enables you to travel at high speeds for long periods of time. You gain the following benefits:</p><ul><li>Increase an ability score of your choice by 1, to a maximum of 20.</li><li>Your Travel Pace doubles, and you can travel at Fast Pace with no penalties.</li><li>When you cast <em><strong>Way of Onmitsu: Shunpo</strong></em>, you gain a +1d4 bonus to the next attack roll you make, twice per round.</li><li>While you are gaining the benefits of a jutsu that increases your movement speed, you cannot make Dexterity checks with penalties, excluding disadvantage.</li><li>You reduce the cost and concentration cost of jutsu that increase your movement speed by -1. This reduction can reduce the concentration cost of the jutsu to 0.</li></ul>",
